{"tid":2072690,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一間正氣按摩店","createTime":"2020-06-20T18:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T01:58:52.000Z","uid":11759,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1a0fb40a9ef6b1b6f193a1b95468c75ca33af7","tid":2072690,"uid":11759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:10:45.000Z","msg":"按摩真係好舒服 按完真係鬆晒...<br />\n特別係連續返工踩10幾日之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說試完一間貌似做街坊生意<br />\n主打養生嘅店...老實講係幾舒服嘅<br />\n不過一做完之後就Sell package <br />\n對於sell package係有啲反感 <br />\n講真一次幾百蚊放鬆吓有乜所謂<br />\n 但package一買就要買10-12次<br />\n其實我真係未必有時間個個月去按<br />\n如果嗰排忙可能真係兩三個月按一次 <br />\n試過都唔錯諗住之後都會逐次按 <br />\n對方竟然話：逐次計你肯定唔會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能因為呢間係試做價啦 所以一定sell <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日喺Facebook /IG都見到好多介紹<br />\n但因為呢次經歷之後應該都唔會再敢試<br />\n唔知絲打有冇啲小店介紹下 乾淨就得<br />\n利伸幾鐘意泰式按摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aafda85a5d6e373ae072328d503cd84657b43ad","tid":2072690,"uid":128271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:18:05.000Z","msg":"元朗有間叫足願美 幾乾淨"},{"pid":"cbfdba28df9bab34384edf6a2643b82c141a120b","tid":2072690,"uid":34084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:20:08.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪去咗足君好按<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1e51a1881e07a1c2b1834df75b6376098deabb","tid":2072690,"uid":154644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:29:36.000Z","msg":"其實一次幾錢到 想鬆下 膊頭"},{"pid":"798c34530d9b693dcd244e85fead2e4f03595248","tid":2072690,"uid":31370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:35:37.000Z","msg":"九龍灣有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c33da7b4750053216a9789fef14291bdf109e9","tid":2072690,"uid":60959,"like":15,"dislike":0,"s